131
00:08:54.411 --> 00:08:57.011
Tapi, kita ada pertandingan tenis besok.

132
00:08:57.011 --> 00:08:58.211
Jangan cemas.

133
00:08:58.211 --> 00:09:01.111
Lihat, Taman Atletik Prefektur ini

134
00:09:01.111 --> 00:09:04.211
