00:24:30.162 --> 00:24:31.562
Selanjutnya dalam Conan,

403
00:24:31.562 --> 00:24:35.762
"Smash Cinta dan Penyelesaian (Bagian 2)"

404
00:24:36.389 --> 00:24:38.589
Petunjuk Conan Selanjutnya:

405
00:24:38.589 --> 00:24:40.689
"Upacara Penghargaan"

406
00:24:40.689 --> 00:24:41.889
